<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Certificate of Authenticity</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .certificate {
            width: 800px;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 10px solid #e0c08d;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
        }

        .certificate::before, .certificate::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            border: 1px solid #e0c08d;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Old English Text MT', cursive;
            color: #a67b3e;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Old English Text MT', cursive;
            color: #a67b3e;
            margin-top: -10px;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #a67b3e;
        }

        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .details label {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 200px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .signature {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .signature span {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border-top: 1px solid #a67b3e;
            padding-top: 5px;
            color: #a67b3e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="certificate">
        <div class="title">Certificate Of Authenticity</div>
        <div class="subtitle">Of Original Art Work</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>This is to certify</p>
            <p>That the artwork identified herein is an original and authentic work of art.</p>
            <p>The artist reserves all copyright and reproduction rights.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <p><label>Title of Work:</label> <span>{{peinture.title}}</span></p>
            <p><label>Artist:</label> <span>{{peinture.name}}</span></p>
            <p><label>Dimensions:</label> <span>{{peinture.width}} x {{peinture.height}} cm (Landscape Orientation)</span></p>
            <p><label>Year Completed:</label> <span>{{peinture.createdAt}}</span></p>
            <p><label>Certified this:</label> <span>{{ "now"|date("d") }}<sup>th</sup></span> Day of: <span>{{ "now"|date("F") }}, {{ "now"|date("Y") }}</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="signature">
            <span>ARTIST SIGNATURE</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
